throws Exception was added to all methods except processOnError(Throwable cause) because I thought it does not make sense to raise an exception on an error handler.
Or we can do like the following style.
try {
    process(data);
    ...
} catch (Throwable ex) {
    Exceptions.throwIfFatal(ex);
    try {
        handler.processOnError(ex);
    } catch (Throwable ex1) {
        Exceptions.throwIfFatal(ex1);
        ex = new CompositeException(ex1, ex);
    }
    cancelAndCleanup();
    abort(ex);
}

